{"tid":1538511,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"敵退我進","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T07:21:06.000Z","uid":34872,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"10d1a4f60bcb3d44704f39d22e01b68eccf4a8af","tid":1538511,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:12:21.000Z","msg":"咁多熟讀毛語錄人士<br />\n而家佢退 撒回就即係退 就係我地進攻拎番曬失去左既野的時候<br />\n97後呢段殖民大家既苦難生活 一定要有回報"},{"pid":"cdb6cb1898161d0e85577cfa500615d828731b40","tid":1538511,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:12:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUGSMa3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUGSMa3.gif&h=1c74332a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【長期抗爭】最簡單有效嘅日常抗爭<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538155</a>"},{"pid":"c6aa26d50a5667d6aa2baa1f9aa43c99fadc4c19","tid":1538511,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:12:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61deaf37ed1822aafb7809f68091ad821bbd02cd","tid":1538511,"uid":33099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:13:06.000Z","msg":"一定要真普選 叫價不二"},{"pid":"4191bf39bef9053a3e52cc28b51e95b19479eee1","tid":1538511,"uid":295304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:14:26.000Z","msg":"有冇見過兇殺案由政府新聞處公佈？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535010</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇埋回覆先留言，因為分析我放咗喺回覆<br />\n<br />\n成個熱門勁多都係講林鄭撤回嘅風，<br />\n但而家佢撤唔撤回都好，831太子站有冇死人、有冇極嚴重傷勢受害人，呢d都係要查啊！唔好俾佢轉移焦點啊！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好認真，點解一路發生咁多件事，都冇話撤回，突然今日會講起？到底呢幾日發生咗咩事逼到佢要做野？係咪真係其實死咗人？就算冇死人，到底情況係幾嚴重？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要求黨鐵交出831太子站完整CCTV記錄啊！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"70f6ff8d5c2267376cbfce2a164682cb99c0b296","tid":1538511,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:15:52.000Z","msg":"唔知大家記唔記得「五大訴求」雛形係點嚟？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538125\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538125</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong><em><div style=\"text-align: center;\">毋忘七烈 千一義 四眼 三十骨折 手腳筋<br />\n721元朗 811警暴 831車廂 雙肺 一裙<br />\n無數屈辱私刑 重傷昏迷<br />\n<br />\n撤回 定性 釋士 究警 普選</div></em></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">港共殺人政權企圖以撤回 <br />\n轉移<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子地鐵傷亡、六警壓脊椎休克昏迷、<br />\n新屋嶺、人主民權法案</span></strong>事件焦點<br />\n醒呀大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 政府帶緊風向</span>"},{"pid":"367210e36c190a9e07b75299159b4cf1c866de80","tid":1538511,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:21:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LgdcLSU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLgdcLSU.jpg&h=7d8fce73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ktasvY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ktasvY.jpg&h=e8e5ebbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WwTmzaZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWwTmzaZ.jpg&h=1a577aad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a889SFe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa889SFe.jpg&h=3fb438bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n機場壓力測試，其實係連「機場」都唔需要入的<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1531743\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1531743</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}